01:03:57.050 --> 01:03:58.704
I've, uh...

01:03:58.747 --> 01:04:00.662
Been thinking about
you a lot recently.

01:04:00.706 --> 01:04:04.057
Yeah, I've been
thinking about you too.

01:04:05.885 --> 01:04:07.626
Um...

01:04:07.669 --> 01:04:08.888
