01:04:08.932 --> 01:04:09.802
Are... Are you busy?

01:04:09.846 --> 01:04:12.674
Uh, no.

01:04:12.718 --> 01:04:15.677
Um, I'm just
shopping for balloons

01:04:15.721 --> 01:04:18.419
