that I purchased.

01:19:05.958 --> 01:19:07.394
That's fucking awesome.

01:19:07.438 --> 01:19:08.700
It really is.

01:19:10.049 --> 01:19:11.703
I think we're gonna be okay.

01:19:13.400 --> 01:19:15.272
